    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>General Description</strong></h2><br>Fear Of The Darkness is a narrative psychological horror game that will push you to face the serious phobias of some patients.<br><br>Play as the enigmatic doctor in charge of treating them, or at least try, it won't be an easy mission.<br><br>Avoid by all means being overwhelmed by the heavy emotional burden of your patients, come out of the Darkness and explore the various corners of the so-called Truth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/5880db56255c872c7aefe0e5feb9763d.avif?t=1730110378\" width=436 height=514 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Setting</strong></h2><br>The main environment of the game is a strange room, where everything changes often, a bit like it is in our nature.<br><br>Be careful, here you will be able to discover many details about the characters' stories after delving into their minds; you will be able to unlock new powers, relax, look around and continue this unusual journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/b9c6c68bd9df29eaec13f229c73d322c.avif?t=1730110378\" width=540 height=540 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2>Go through the different phases of the game and rummages through the patients' rarefied memories, always in search of Clarity.<br><br>Explore these 4 intriguing stories, each with its own unique gameplay:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> a platform phase in which you will have to jump carefully to reach the end of the various paths, but remember that nothing lasts forever...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/91e72b9f2aac114d7a325ae733505812.avif?t=1730110378\" width=540 height=540 /></span><br><br></li><li> a phase where you will encounter something or someone in the dark that is not real, or maybe it is?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/4bb738a30acb5e9f054afe56502aba2d.avif?t=1730110378\" width=540 height=540 /></span><br><br></li><li> a fast-paced phase in which you will be encouraged to run and escape, but escape from what?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/f08405b923e78ec502c1a7755e562e24.avif?t=1730110378\" width=540 height=540 /></span><br><br></li><li> a puzzle phase where you will have to use your skills to get to the goal, or perhaps you will prefer to linger for a long time?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/fa04855ca622de2bdf8dd3ce25343aef.avif?t=1730110378\" width=540 height=540 /></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Final Advice</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Clarity could help you...</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793200/extras/cf3ab057ae9c04b28cfff912a0d6b160.avif?t=1730110378\" width=540 height=540 /></span>",
